      <title>由于伊朗风险挥之不去，美国库存数据公布前油价小幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场预计美国原油库存可能增加，并等待以色列对伊朗周末袭击事件的反应，油价小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 23:21:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储押注推动抛售后，国债上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球金融市场恢复了相对平静的感觉，在押注美联储将在更长时间内维持较高利率的推动下，债券出现抛售，随后出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 22:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
